                                        <li><span style="color: #EF5350;">&#9679;</span> <b>Cash</b> &mdash; negative free cash flow (cash burn)</li>
                                        <li><span style="color: #AB47BC;">&#9679;</span> <b>Decl</b> &mdash; revenue &amp; margin both declining QoQ</li>
